title.rendered: Georgia Primary Voting Shows Strong Democratic Enthusiasm Despite No Top-of-Ticket Competitive Races

content.rendered:
ATLANTA — Today, Abrams for Governor released a memo from Campaign Manager Lauren Groh-Wargo detailing and analyzing high levels of Democratic voting in the May 24 primary leading into the general election.

Read the memo at: staceyabrams.com/primaryturnout

###
